				=09
					<div id=3D"mw-content-text" class=3D"mw-body-content"><div class=3D"mw=
-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang=3D"en" dir=3D"ltr"><div class=3D"shortd=
escription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style=3D"display:none">Bas=
ketball statistic</div>
<p>
In <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basketball" title=3D"Basketball=
">basketball</a>, <b>true shooting percentage</b> is an <a href=3D"https://=
en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Advanced_statistics_in_basketball" title=3D"Advanced =
statistics in basketball">advanced statistic</a> that measures a player's <=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Efficiency_(basketball)" title=3D"E=
fficiency (basketball)">efficiency</a> at shooting the ball.<sup id=3D"cite=
_ref-1" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/True_s=
hooting_percentage#cite_note-1"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>1<span=
 class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> It is intended to more accuratel=
y calculate a player's shooting than <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Field_goal_percentage" title=3D"Field goal percentage">field goal percen=
tage</a>, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Free_throw_percentage" c=
lass=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Free throw percentage">free throw percentage<=
/a>, and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Three-point_field_goal_pe=
rcentage" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Three-point field goal percentage"=
>three-point field goal percentage</a> taken individually.  Two- and three-=
point field goals and free throws are all considered in its calculation.  I=
t is abbreviated <b>TS%</b>.
</p><p>It is calculated by: <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-elemen=
t-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=
=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" altt=
ext=3D"{\displaystyle TS\%=3D{\frac {PTS}{2(FGA+0.44\times FTA)}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>T</mi>
        <mi>S</mi>
        <mi mathvariant=3D"normal">%<!-- % --></mi>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mi>P</mi>
              <mi>T</mi>
              <mi>S</mi>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <mn>2</mn>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
              <mi>F</mi>
              <mi>G</mi>
              <mi>A</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>0.44</mn>
              <mo>=C3=97<!-- =C3=97 --></mo>
              <mi>F</mi>
              <mi>T</mi>
              <mi>A</mi>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle TS\%=3D{\frac=
 {PTS}{2(FGA+0.44\times FTA)}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/2457f989eca3319e1d8ffef108615c2f9290eab9" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -2.671ex; width:32.223ex; height:6.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle TS=
\%=3D{\frac {PTS}{2(FGA+0.44\times FTA)}}}"></span>
</p><p>where:
</p>
<ul><li>PTS =3D points scored,</li>
<li>FGA =3D field goal attempts,</li>
<li>FTA =3D free throw attempts <sup id=3D"cite_ref-2" class=3D"reference">=
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/True_shooting_percentage#cite_note=
-2"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>2<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</s=
pan></a></sup></li></ul>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"National_Basketball_Associa=
tion">National Basketball Association</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><s=
pan class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedi=
a.org/w/index.php?title=3DTrue_shooting_percentage&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;se=
ction=3D1" title=3D"Edit section: National Basketball Association"><span>ed=
it</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<div class=3D"thumb tmulti tright"><div class=3D"thumbinner multiimageinner=
" style=3D"width:242px;max-width:242px"><div class=3D"trow"><div class=3D"t=
single" style=3D"width:131px;max-width:131px"><div class=3D"thumbimage" sty=
le=3D"height:160px;overflow:hidden"><span typeof=3D"mw:File"><a href=3D"htt=
ps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Stephen_Curry_2016_(cropped).jpg" class=3D"=
mw-file-description"><img alt=3D"" src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wiki=
pedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Stephen_Curry_2016_%28cropped%29.jpg/250px-Stephen=
_Curry_2016_%28cropped%29.jpg" decoding=3D"async" width=3D"129" height=3D"1=
