ephen Curry</a></div></div><div class=3D"tsingle" style=3D"width:107px;max-=
width:107px"><div class=3D"thumbimage" style=3D"height:160px;overflow:hidde=
n"><span typeof=3D"mw:File"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:K=
evin_Durant_(Wizards_v._Warriors,_1-24-2019)_(cropped).jpg" class=3D"mw-fil=
e-description"><img alt=3D"" src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/=
commons/thumb/3/3a/Kevin_Durant_%28Wizards_v._Warriors%2C_1-24-2019%29_%28c=
ropped%29.jpg/120px-Kevin_Durant_%28Wizards_v._Warriors%2C_1-24-2019%29_%28=
cropped%29.jpg" decoding=3D"async" width=3D"105" height=3D"161" class=3D"mw=
-file-element" data-file-width=3D"872" data-file-height=3D"1336"></a></span=
></div><div class=3D"thumbcaption text-align-center"><a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Durant" title=3D"Kevin Durant">Kevin Durant</a></d=
iv></div></div></div></div>
<p>Several players in the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National=
_Basketball_Association" title=3D"National Basketball Association">National=
 Basketball Association</a> (NBA) record consistently high TS%, demonstrati=
ng their ability to efficiently score points for their teams. <a href=3D"ht=
tps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Curry" title=3D"Stephen Curry">Stephen =
Curry</a> of the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golden_State_Warr=
iors" title=3D"Golden State Warriors">Golden State Warriors</a> and <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Durant" title=3D"Kevin Durant">Kevi=
n Durant</a> of the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Houston_Rocket=
s" title=3D"Houston Rockets">Houston Rockets</a> have career true shooting =
percentages of 62.6% and 61.9%, respectively, making them two of the most e=
fficient scorers in NBA history.=20
</p><p>In addition, big men like <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/C=
lint_Capela" title=3D"Clint Capela">Clint Capela</a> of the <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Houston_Rockets" title=3D"Houston Rockets">Housto=
n Rockets</a> have also posted high TS% due to their ability to score effic=
iently around the basket and convert <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Free_throw" title=3D"Free throw">free throws</a> at a high rate.
</p><p>In the WNBA, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sylvia_Fowles"=
 title=3D"Sylvia Fowles">Sylvia Fowles</a> and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipe=
dia.org/wiki/Jonquel_Jones" title=3D"Jonquel Jones">Jonquel Jones</a> have =
recorded career true shooting percentages of 63.6% and 61.7% respectively.
</p>
